title: Bobby Bones vs. Jameson Rogers In 'Bop It'! + Raymundo's Awkward Country Artist Handshake + Eddie's Son Has A Locked Diary
itunes:title: Bobby Bones vs. Jameson Rogers In 'Bop It'! + Raymundo's Awkward Country Artist Handshake + Eddie's Son Has A Locked Diary
description:
Jameson Rogers stops by the studio to perform a few songs including “Some Girls” and his new one “Good Dogs”. Bobby then challenges him to a heated battle of 'Bop It'! Raymundo reveals what country artist he had an awkward, fumbling, handshake with recently. Plus, we recently talked about Amy’s daughter wanting a locked diary…well, turns out Eddie’s son has one too and Eddie had no idea!
